material.mattext:
i. Here are the possible outcomes in each of the two events:
       A={(GBB), (BGB), (BBG)}
       C={(BGG), (GBG), (GGB)}
ii. The two events do not overlap, they have no outcome in common.
iii. Based on ii, the events are disjoint - they can never occur together.

